MID_支援_ヒノカ_レオン_Ａ: $t1$Wmヒノカ|7$Wmレオン|3$w0|$Wsヒノカ|$WaPrince Leon.$k\n$Wsレオン|$WaPrincess Hinoka?$k\n$Wsヒノカ|$Wa$E怒,|Do you remember what you\nsaid to me a few days ago?$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E怒,|The fact that you fight alone...\nWas that it?$k\n$Wsヒノカ|$Wa$E苦,汗|Yes...$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E通常,|Yes, I did in fact say so.$k\n$Wsヒノカ|$WaI...don't intend on fighting alone.$k$pI fight alongside my comrades\nand soldiers, that much I know.$k$p$E怒,|But, I also believe in only my own power.\nThat's not it, I can only rely on my own$k$ppower... That is what I meant, I suppose.$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E怒,|Why would that be?$k\n$Wsヒノカ|$Wa$E通常,|I am afraid of relying too much\non my comrades and soldiers.$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E通常,|You're afraid of relying on them?$k\n$Wsヒノカ|$Wa$E苦,汗|It's easy to rely on someone. However for\nme to rely on someone means putting them$k$pin danger...and when I imagine such\nthings I can't help but feel afraid.$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E怒,|So depending on someone brings one\nunder death's embrace...or so to speak.$k\n$Wsヒノカ|$Wa$E怒,|Do you think I'm mistaken?$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E通常,|No, you are not at fault.$k$p$E笑,|In fact, I finally understand why\neveryone trusts you so much.$k\n$Wsヒノカ|$Wa$E通常,|…………$k\n$Wsレオン|$WaYou want to protect everyone,\nmore than anyone.$k\n$Wsヒノカ|$Wa$E怒,|Everyone's presence makes me stronger. \nThat's why I want to be strong for them.$k$pI apologize that I am not\nof use to you, Prince Leon.$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E怒,|There is no helping it.$k$p$E笑,|I will fight alongside you as you are.\nI hope we can get along well.$k\n$Wsヒノカ|$Wa$E笑,|Prince Leon...\nYes, I am in your hands.$k
MID_支援_ヒノカ_レオン_Ｓ: $t1$Wmヒノカ|7$Wmレオン|3$w0|$Wsレオン|$WaPrincess Hinoka, has the thought of\nmarriage ever crossed your mind?$k\n$Wsヒノカ|$Wa$E苦,照汗|Prince Leon?! This is so sudden?!\nWe're in battle right now!!$k$pThis isn't the time to be worrying\nourselves with such things!!$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E怒,|When you are thinking of someone,\nthe time and place matters not.$k\n$Wsヒノカ|$WaThat might be, but...$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E通常,|I knew it was rude of me...\nHowever, I wanted to know.$k\n$Wsヒノカ|$Wa$E怒,照汗|I-If you really want to know...\nI don't mind telling you...$k\n$Wsレオン|$WaIf you will, I am listening$k\n$Wsヒノカ|$Wa$E通常,照汗|W-well I am a girl after all...\nSo, marriage has crossed my mind...$k$p$E苦,汗|However who would ever love...\nA warrior girl like me...$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E笑,照|But, I have fallen for you.\nPrincess Hinoka.$k\n$Wsヒノカ|$Wa$E苦,照汗|Wha?!$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E怒,照|I love you, Princess Hinoka.\nMay I take your hand in marriage?$k\n$Wsヒノカ|$WaYou...love me?$k$p$E怒,照汗|Stop with the jokes! Such a smart man like\nyou with a girl that only knows how to fight.$k\n$Wsレオン|$WaThis is no joke. I love you from the\nbottom of my heart, Princess Hinoka.$k$p$E笑,照|Your courage and kindness\ndrew me towards you.$k\n$Wsヒノカ|$WaPrince Leon...$k$p$E苦,照汗|But, we're both from opposing kingdoms...\nMarriage between us would not be simple.$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E怒,照|When you're thinking about someone,\nones origin or status does not matter.$k$pPrincess Hinoka, please accept this ring.$k\n$Wsヒノカ|$Wa$E怒,照|Even if we get married...I am me.\nI won't change, you know?$k$p$E通常,照汗|Well...I'll do my best as a wife but I'll\nprobably be on the battlefield more so$k$pthan in the castle...$k$p$E怒,照汗|Are you still okay with that?!$k\n$Wsレオン|$Wa$E笑,照|Even if you object,\nI do not plan on retreating.$k$pFor I have fallen in\nlove with a female warrior.$k\n$Wsヒノカ|$Wa$E笑,照|You're such a strange\nperson...but I'm glad...$k$pPrince Leon...$k\n$Wsレオン|$WaSo, you accept my proposal?$k\n$Wsヒノカ|$Wa$Eキメ,照|Yes. I am in your care.$k
